<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Verify Your Email</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .otp-box {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      background-color: #e9f5ff;
      color: #007bff;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <h2> Welcome to {{appName}}</h2>
    </div>
    <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>
    <p>Thanks for signing up! To complete your registration, please use the OTP below:</p>

    <div class="otp-box">{{otp}}</div>

    <p>This OTP is valid for the next 10 minutes. Please do not share this code with anyone.</p>

    <p>If you didnâ€™t request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
